FBIS4-58075 "drnes084_j_94031" FBIS-NES-94-084 Daily Report 1 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Al-Bid Briefs Syria's Asad on Situation Al-Bid Briefs Syria's Asad on Situation EA0205064094 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 1 May 94 EA0205064094 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Brother 'Ali Salim al-Bid, deputy chairman of the Presidential Council and secretary general of the Yemeni Socialist Party, conducted a telephone conversation with his brother Hafiz al-Asad, the president of the Syrian Arab Republic, whom he briefed on deveopments affecting the Yemeni arena in the context of military interactions aimed at plunging the country into a destructive civil war.
